{"tid":102650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廿五歲美女教師色誘十六歲少年 多次在公園瘋狂打野戰","createTime":"2017-01-31T18:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T17:41:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f556567317f1e253901b34b96f8e155c80bd975","tid":102650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:38:25.000Z","msg":"Married teacher, 25, had sex with pupil, 16, in her home and the park after seducing him <br />\n<br />\nA MARRIED sex predator teacher who seduced an underage teenager into having sex in her home and also a state park has been jailed for just one year. <br />\n<br />\nHer legal team was able to negotiate a plea deal in Berea, Kentucky. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/nintchdbpict000298190247.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fnintchdbpict000298190247.jpg&h=f18aa06a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nTeacher Brandi Lynn Vaughn was sentenced to just one year in jail <br />\n<br />\nNow Brandi Lynn Vaughn, a former Madison Southern High School teacher accused of twice having sexual relations with the teenager admitted just one felony charge. <br />\n<br />\nThe 25-year-old admitted using an electronic device to induce a minor to engage in sexual activities. <br />\n<br />\nThe Class D felony can be punished by one to five years in prison and he eligible for parole after serving 20 percent of her term. <br />\n<br />\nBacking the plea agreement, Judge William Clouse agreed six other Class D felony charges against Vaughn be dismissed. <br />\n<br />\nThese were two counts of first-degree sexual abuse; two counts of third-degree sodomy; one count of third-degree rape and one count of evidence tampering. <br />\n<br />\nVaughn, who taught science, was arrested in August 2015. <br />\n<br />\nThe Richmond Register reports the teacher confessed to investigators to twice having sexual encounters with a male student, then 16, according to a Berea Police Department news release. <br />\n<br />\nOne incident took place at a state park, while the other took place at the then married teacher&rsquo;s home. <br />\n<br />\nThe state age of consent is 16 providing the other person is under 21. <br />\n<br />\nThe newspaper said before starting at the school, she worked as a science, technology, engineering and math mentor at the high school through a Berea College program. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to Whitaker&rsquo;s LinkedIn profile, she was once a youth program volunteer for the Berea Baptist Church, the paper reports, and a social media post shows the church hosted a wedding shower for her in March 2013."},{"pid":"e9c8fc977fcfd6242278fbe2c0036d591d4fe1fd","tid":102650,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:39:17.000Z","msg":"今次睇落ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20186c8ea967b47c151c10035bbfb84d200d6e97","tid":102650,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:39:21.000Z","msg":"I WANT TO BE THE PREY"},{"pid":"1ce7bca4a1b94a88706d9e2fb3c5f8fdd4274f36","tid":102650,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:39:48.000Z","msg":"快點強姦樓下個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392a857b61e5463d1211e2a406153a63a6938f4a","tid":102650,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:40:05.000Z","msg":"快點強姦我！"},{"pid":"b7d9474af11ec84a7b7847f5b09cf892d52903b3","tid":102650,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:52:59.000Z","msg":"快點強姦樓上個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b3c35bffd05ebc97d64f1cfbf665c8aef81573","tid":102650,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"